| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1617 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3ff5d170-9bf2-55e4-a550-c5bd0b1c26fa"
